《'''馬達加斯加爆走企鵝'''》（{{lang-en|''Penguins of Madagascar''}}）是一部2014年美国3D电脑动画动作喜剧电影<ref name=DWAStarsAlign />，为《[[马达加斯加_(电影)|马达加斯加]]》电影系列的分支之作。[[梦工厂动画|梦工厂动画]]制作，北美和其他国家地区由[[20世纪福斯|20世纪福斯]]发行<ref name=ColliderHomePenguinsNYCC>{{cite web|last1=Nemiroff|first1=Perri|title=HOME and PENGUINS OF MADAGASCAR Comic-Con Panel Recap: New Footage, Evil Scientist Octopus, 28-Second Alien Invasion and More|url=http://collider.com/penguins-of-madagascar-comic-con-panel-recap-home/|publisher=Collider.com|accessdate=October 14, 2014|date=October 12, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016185338/http://collider.com/penguins-of-madagascar-comic-con-panel-recap-home/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，中国大陆由[[东方梦工厂|东方梦工厂]]发行。

[[西蒙·J·史密斯|西蒙·J·史密斯]]和[[埃里克·达尼尔|埃里克·达尼尔]]联合执导，[[Michael_Colton|Michael Colton]]和[[John_Aboud|John Aboud]]编剧。主要配音员有[[Tom_McGrath_(animator)|Tom McGrath]]、[[Chris_Miller_(animator)|Chris Miller]]、[[Conrad_Vernon|Conrad Vernon]]、[[Christopher_Knights|Christopher Knights]]、[[Benedict_Cumberbatch|Benedict Cumberbatch]]、[[John_Malkovich|John Malkovich]]和[[Ken_Jeong|Ken Jeong]]。中国大陆和美国分别于2014年11月14日、26日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/10/penguins-of-madagascar-will-hit-china-before-opening-stateside-857265/|script-title=en:‘Penguins Of Madagascar’ Will Open In China Before U.S. - Deadline|date=October 21, 2014|work=Deadline|accessdate=October 22, 2014|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211183845/https://deadline.com/2014/10/penguins-of-madagascar-will-hit-china-before-opening-stateside-857265/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==剧情==
[[章鱼|章鱼]]戴夫最初在[[水族馆|水族馆]]裡受到不少游客的喜爱，可是渐渐地游客都喜爱上了[[企鹅|企鹅]]，这让戴夫受到很大的冷落，自尊心得到严重打击的他从此对企鹅们怀恨在心。后来戴夫开始实施他的报仇计划，他决心发明一种药水——變怪物精華液，它能让企鹅都变成丑陋的怪物以便受到人类的讨厌。随着越来越多的企鹅都遭到戴夫成员的[[绑架|绑架]]，四位企鹅：老大、卡哇伊、涼快和菜鳥，联手以灰狼为首的“放風所”四成员，与邪恶的章鱼们展开了一次激烈较量<ref name=DWAStarsAlign>{{cite news|title=The Stars Align For 2015 DreamWorks Animation Films|url=http://new.pitchengine.com/pitches/9478b619-99eb-433c-b1e3-41579d15230a|accessdate=January 19, 2014|newspaper=Pitch Engine|date=August 15, 2013|author=DreamWorks Animation|archive-date=2018-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180717100213/https://new.pitchengine.com/pitches/9478b619-99eb-433c-b1e3-41579d15230a|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ColliderConRecap>{{cite web|last1=Goldberg|first1=Matt|title=PENGUINS OF MADAGASCAR Comic-Con Panel Recap: A Great DreamWorks Animated Film Might Be on the Way|url=http://collider.com/penguins-of-madagascar-comic-con-panel-recap/|publisher=Collider.com|accessdate=July 25, 2014|date=July 24, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141012213419/http://collider.com/penguins-of-madagascar-comic-con-panel-recap/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

